Application to ivy leagues

tommyshelby 6 replies15 threads Junior Member
April 23 in College Admissions
Can i apply to ivy leagues before my 12th grade results coming out?
April 23
4 replies
0 · Reply · Share

Replies to: Application to ivy leagues

  • #1
    TomSrOfBoston 15735 replies1052 threads Senior Member
    April 23
    Are you international? In the US students apply to colleges at the start of 12th grade. They would then send in first marking period grades when available.
    April 23
    0 · Reply · Share
  • #2
    Lindagaf 10496 replies577 threads Super Moderator
    April 23
    You hav to apply to college by whatever their deadline is. There is no advantage to applying to any Ivy League college before their deadline if it means your application is weaker because you can’t include your grade 12 results.

    If your school doesn’t release those results until after deadlines, those colleges will probably be aware of how your country handles this, so they might ask you to provide predicted results.
    April 23
    0 · Reply · Share
  • #3
    tommyshelby 6 replies15 threads Junior Member
    April 24
    Thanks a lot for replying. Am a student in india and our results come out by August so what procedure will i have to go thorough in order to apply.
    April 24
    0 · Reply · Share
  • #4
    tommyshelby 6 replies15 threads Junior Member
    April 24
    yes i am an international student

post_text.surface_form: Can i apply to ivy leagues before my 12th grade results coming out?
Are you international? In the US students apply to colleges at the start of 12th grade. They would then send in first marking period grades when available.

You hav to apply to college by whatever their deadline is. There is no advantage to applying to any Ivy League college before their deadline if it means your application is weaker because you can’t include your grade 12 results. If your school doesn’t release those results until after deadlines, those colleges will probably be aware of how your country handles this, so they might ask you to provide predicted results.
